reviewText: Would order from again. Love this series
This is one of my all time favorite shows and the DVD's perform very well. Clear picture and good sound.
Every show has me in suspense and cracking up at the same time. Lots of humor and suspense. Very well made with great acting and dialog.
Love this show. Unlike anything else I've ever seen
It is a great series.  However, the DVDs that I received were defective.  My money was returned, but I still want to buy them.
Star quality... Cast is phenomenal and the script is always intriguing.  A MUST SEE... Tatiana Maslany is brilliant and deserves an award for acting.
